reviewText: The movie itself is 'beautiful' in every way--crystal clear in detail!  However a "Bonus" 12 song Christmas CD is missing/ not included in the set. The set contains (1) Blu-Ray DVD movie; (1) Regular movie in DVD format and (1) DVD of special features. Please contact me via my E-mail: dreamboy00745@yahoo.com.  I thank you & await your reply!

Favorite family movie that brings back memories of family over the years.  Scenery is beautiful.  costumes are gorgeous.  Vera Ellen is one fabulous dancer.  check out George Chakiris before West Side Story.  does include smoking but....we all know better in 2018!  Loved the extra background interviews.  Wholesome family entertainment with brilliant music, casting and entertainment value.
